00:22:53,921 --> 00:22:58,704
four transducers that were put into the experience and they were discrete channels and floor zones

289
00:22:59,044 --> 00:23:05,106
and they didn't just rumble. We were actually able to send specific audio to them in those

290
00:23:05,126 --> 00:23:09,348
frequencies so we could really shape them to work with what you're hearing in the headphones.

